name: Stay a While
description: Stay A While Frontend holds the front-end development source of React-Redux app that allows users to reserve an apartment or home. The app allows users to list their properties.

name: Budget Tracker
description: Mobile web application where you can manage your budget: you have a list of transactions associated with a category, so that you can see how much money you spent and on what.

name: Food Recipes App
description: The app keeps track of all your recipes and ingredients. It will allow you to save ingredients, create recipes, and generate a shopping list based on what you have and what you are missing from a recipe.

name: Movie Max
description: A web app for movies using TVmaze API for showing movies and its details. The webapp have 2 user interfaces. A home page showing a list of movies items that you can like. A popup window with more data about the movie that you can use to comment on it.

name: Beauty Summit
description: A webpage recreated based on the design by Cindy-Shin-in-Behance

name: Awesome Books
description: An application that stores a list of books added to the browser's localstorage and display their title and authors on the page.

name: Space Traveler's Hub
description: The website models a space website that fetches data from real live data from spaceX and displays it on the UI. Missions and Reserve Rockets can be joined and reserved respectively, and are displayed in My profile page.
